fiduswriter-server (4.1.0~beta.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * Upstream version 4.1.0-beta.1
  * Single package with all modules included
  * Bundled Python 3.14.5 compiled from source
  * All dependencies and optional modules included:
    - fiduswriter-books
    - fiduswriter-citation-api-import
    - fiduswriter-languagetool
    - fiduswriter-ojs
    - fiduswriter-pandoc
    - fiduswriter-phplist
    - fiduswriter-gitrepo-export
    - fiduswriter-payment-paddle
    - fiduswriter-website
  * Works on Ubuntu 20.04+, Debian 11+ (no Python 3.11+ required)
  * Add systemd service integration
  * Self-contained package (~250-300 MB)

